title: 351. Andy & DJ CTI: Nancy Pelosi Departs From Taiwan, Capitol Rioter Gets 7 Years In Jail & Liquor Store Owner Shoots Would-Be Robber
itunes:title: 351. Andy & DJ CTI: Nancy Pelosi Departs From Taiwan, Capitol Rioter Gets 7 Years In Jail & Liquor Store Owner Shoots Would-Be Robber
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Nancy Pelosi's departure from Taiwan after her 19-hour visit, a capitol rioter receiving seven years for bringing a gun into the capitol on January 6th, and the 80-year-old California liquor store owner shooting a would-be robber.
